div.p:
The Embassy at Habana has submitted for the Department’s consideration an
                    additional draft agreementDated February 25, 1943;
                        transmitted to the Department in Embassy’s despatch No. 2314, February 26,
                        not printed. with Cuba (in effect are agreements of June 19,
                        1942;

                            Foreign Relations, 1942, vol. vi, p. 267. September 7,
                        1942;

                            Ibid., p. 283. February 1, 1943
                        Supra.
                    ) which has been found necessary to iron out several minor problems. The
                    draft has received general approval in the Cuban Ministry of State, although it
                    is likely that it may suggest some specific changes.
